 Review comment:
   According to the spec (https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/34b9bb2ca2e3adc256a9876e513281fc348afaea/format/Schema.fbs#L136-L137), the values for Date64Type should be multiples of 86400000.
   
   And if we should follow that, the pretty print should probably only show the date (although that would hide "invalid" dates) 

